  --   * (12)         pair with (12345);
  --   * (123)        pair with (124)(35);
  --   * (123)(45)    pair with (124);
  --   * (1234)       pair with (12345);
  --   * (12)(34)     pair with (1354);
  --   * (12345)      pair with (12).
  -- TODO: in each case verify that the closure is `⊤` (e.g. using the
  -- fact that `A_5` is generated by 3-cycles, and an odd element plus
  -- `A_5` give all of `S_5`).
  sorry

end Imc1998P2
